Click "Metric filters" tab
‚úÖ Expected: You should see 5 metric filters


Check Alarm Status

Go to CloudWatch ‚Üí Alarms
‚úÖ Expected: You should see 5 alarms, with "Security Group Changes" possibly in ALARM state


Verify Email Notifications

Check your email inbox
‚úÖ Expected: You should receive email notification about security group changes


Test Dashboard

